data.description: Welcome to this custom built rambler sitting on just over 10 acres. If you're looking for a quiet country setting, it doesn't get any better than this. Many trees have been planted for a wind break and future privacy. Relax on your covered front porch with a morning cup of coffee. Upon entering the home, you are greeted by highly desired open living spaces. The gourmet kitchen boasts a center island, granite tops, soft close hinges on the cabinetry and a corner pantry. Walking in from the garage, you will love the spacious mud room, half bathroom and separate laundry room. The primary bedroom is separate from the two additional main level bedrooms for privacy. Tasteful en suite bathroom that features a double vanity, soaking tub and a separate shower. You'll be sure to enjoy a 4 stall attached garage plus a 26'x36' heated detached garage to house all your toys. An additional 15'x24' metal shed provides more storage. Don't miss out on your opportunity to own this wonderful property.
